00:00:31.820 --> 00:00:34.740
=Twin Fates=

00:00:34.740 --> 00:00:38.140
=Episode 3=
(Keep Your Hand Steady. Show No Mercy)

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:40.520
I will never cooperate
with anyone again.

00:00:41.240 --> 00:00:42.120
I'm warning you,

00:00:42.720 --> 00:00:44.160
keep your place,

00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:46.720
and you may live a little longer.

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:51.120
Aren't you curious

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:52.720
how I know all of this?

00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:55.560
The pact,

00:00:55.880 --> 00:00:56.680
the sacrifice,

00:00:58.040 --> 00:00:58.840
and the Sacred Temple.

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:01.160
The Scarlet Flame Clan's Sacred Temple
chose me.

00:01:04.560 --> 00:01:06.280
Go down this road.
It leads to the mortal realm.

00:01:06.880 --> 00:01:07.440
Off you go.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:10.280
(Hmph! Twin-soul Contract?)

00:01:10.720 --> 00:01:12.920
(I will find a way to extract
the Xuanzhu Jade)

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:13.920
(and save my clan.)

00:01:15.540 --> 00:01:18.500
(Three days later, Mortal Realm)

00:01:20.900 --> 00:01:23.200
(Lord Yi's Residence)

00:01:23.200 --> 00:01:24.600
Your Lordship!

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:26.360
We have news about Miss Qingci!

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:27.520
Stand right there.

00:01:40.580 --> 00:01:43.180
(Ji Yuanying, daughter
of Lord Yi's concubine)

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:48.680
If the world does me wrong,

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:51.040
I'll take justice

00:01:51.040 --> 00:01:52.480
into my own hands.

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:55.560
I will settle the scores
with each and every one of them.

00:01:56.600 --> 00:01:58.040
I'll settle the grievance with blood,

00:01:58.560 --> 00:01:59.840
burn my enemies with fire.

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:05.000
This time,

00:02:05.880 --> 00:02:07.080
I seize my fate

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:09.480
with my own hands.

00:02:24.280 --> 00:02:25.040
Who are you people?

00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:26.560
What do you want?

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:29.640
You don't need to know.

00:02:30.160 --> 00:02:31.040
Because

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:33.640
you won't leave here alive.

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:38.520
Do you know who I am?

00:02:38.840 --> 00:02:39.680
If I die,

00:02:39.960 --> 00:02:41.120
none of you will get away.

00:02:41.720 --> 00:02:42.840
That's fine.

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:45.040
I will scar your face,

00:02:45.320 --> 00:02:47.640
so no one will recognize you.

00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:50.560
In the end, you'll still
be a missing person.

00:02:51.760 --> 00:02:52.960
(Still a missing person?)

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:54.680
(The letter)

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:56.560
(should've reached
Lord Yi's Residence by now.)

00:02:57.600 --> 00:02:58.280
(Looks like)

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:00.440
(someone doesn't want me to go back.)

00:03:01.240 --> 00:03:02.080
(What should I do?)

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:09.800
What are you trying to do?

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:12.920
Since you're eager to lose your face,

00:03:13.520 --> 00:03:14.800
I'll grant your wish.

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.560
(Finally, he's here.)

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:09.440
What are you waiting for?

00:04:09.720 --> 00:04:10.520
Get him.

00:04:27.240 --> 00:04:28.320
Back then,

00:04:28.640 --> 00:04:30.880
Ji Qingci was already dead.

00:04:31.360 --> 00:04:32.400
Do you think

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:35.240
(Du Ya)
this one is an imposter?

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:39.720
Real or not,

00:04:40.640 --> 00:04:42.960
now that she's entered
Lord Yi's Residence,

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:45.120
she's nothing but prey

00:04:45.920 --> 00:04:47.600
in our grasp.

00:05:49.200 --> 00:05:50.280
Thank you.

00:05:53.840 --> 00:05:55.880
If not for the Xuanzhu Jade inside you,

00:05:56.440 --> 00:05:57.760
you'd be dead already.

00:06:20.400 --> 00:06:22.240
No. Please don't!

00:06:27.200 --> 00:06:28.000
Tell me.

00:06:28.400 --> 00:06:29.400
Who sent you?

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:33.800
Tell me!

00:06:48.800 --> 00:06:49.840
Keep your hand steady.

00:06:52.520 --> 00:06:53.520
Show no mercy.

00:07:08.680 --> 00:07:09.680
If you want to take revenge,

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:12.040
you can't avoid blood.

00:07:27.380 --> 00:07:29.860
(Ying)

00:07:31.640 --> 00:07:32.640
(Ji Yuanying.)

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:34.720
(It's her.)

00:07:41.720 --> 00:07:42.520
Show me the way.

00:07:47.320 --> 00:07:48.440
Why stop me?

00:07:53.280 --> 00:07:53.960
What?

00:07:54.480 --> 00:07:57.960
Can't the mighty Scarlet Flame Lord of War
drive a carriage?

00:08:15.200 --> 00:08:16.240
You came in,

00:08:16.520 --> 00:08:17.760
but who's driving?

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:20.040
Fate.

00:08:26.200 --> 00:08:27.640
Have you heard of this?

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:30.280
Fate must be grasped in your own hand.

00:08:37.220 --> 00:08:41.460
(Lord Yi's Residence)

00:08:44.620 --> 00:08:46.580
(Lord Yi)

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:52.280
Here's Lord Yi's Residence.

00:09:01.900 --> 00:09:04.500
(Lord Yi's Residence)

00:09:04.680 --> 00:09:05.880
(Lord Yi's Residence.)

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:07.920
(It's finally starting.)

00:09:09.440 --> 00:09:10.960
(I will make you pay blood)

00:09:10.960 --> 00:09:12.800
(for blood.)

00:09:26.440 --> 00:09:29.760
Qingci, look at this.

00:09:34.840 --> 00:09:35.720
Do you like it?

00:09:36.920 --> 00:09:37.720
Yes.

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:46.840
My dear Ci.

00:09:48.680 --> 00:09:49.840
It's Ci.

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:52.480
My dear Ci.

00:09:56.960 --> 00:09:58.440
Fa... Father.

00:09:58.720 --> 00:09:59.400
Ci,

00:10:00.320 --> 00:10:01.280
you've suffered

00:10:03.160 --> 00:10:04.720
all these years.

00:10:13.640 --> 00:10:14.840
Who is he?

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:16.560
Father,

00:10:16.560 --> 00:10:19.760
this is my guard,

00:10:20.440 --> 00:10:21.240
Feng.

00:10:23.120 --> 00:10:24.240
He's been protecting me

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:25.560
these years out there.

00:10:26.080 --> 00:10:27.640
Alright. Hurry and prepare...

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:28.840
I'll go warm

00:10:31.280 --> 00:10:32.760
Her Highness's bed.

00:10:36.360 --> 00:10:36.920
You!

00:10:38.520 --> 00:10:39.960
The mountain mists are heavy.

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:42.440
Feng always gathered firewood
to keep our house warm.

00:10:42.800 --> 00:10:43.960
I'm sorry about that, Father.

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:48.160
Qingci,

00:10:48.800 --> 00:10:51.080
this is your elder sister, Ji Yuanying.

00:10:51.880 --> 00:10:53.120
Do you remember her?

00:10:53.840 --> 00:10:54.760
Of course I do.

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:56.960
When I came back,

00:10:56.960 --> 00:10:58.400
I saw a small trinket

00:10:58.400 --> 00:11:00.840
and thought it would suit her.

00:11:04.540 --> 00:11:06.980
(Ying)

00:11:11.960 --> 00:11:13.440
You're so thoughtful, Qingci.

00:11:14.160 --> 00:11:16.320
Father, Qingci's just returned

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:17.560
from a long journey.

00:11:17.560 --> 00:11:19.880
She should get some rest now.

00:11:20.280 --> 00:11:21.040
Oh.

00:11:21.240 --> 00:11:22.960
Yes.

00:11:24.760 --> 00:11:25.560
Qingci.

00:11:32.400 --> 00:11:33.200
That way.

00:11:38.400 --> 00:11:40.360
Qingci, this is your room.

00:12:02.238 --> 00:12:03.798
What exactly are you?

00:12:06.520 --> 00:12:07.320
Me?

00:12:14.920 --> 00:12:16.600
Where did you get

00:12:17.640 --> 00:12:19.160
that half pendant?

00:12:20.360 --> 00:12:22.480
You can't possibly be Ji Qingci.

00:12:23.760 --> 00:12:25.480
Who are you?

00:12:30.120 --> 00:12:31.480
Who do you think

00:12:32.160 --> 00:12:33.200
I am?

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:44.840
Your guard? Feng?

00:12:45.560 --> 00:12:47.040
Since you have doubts,

00:12:47.480 --> 00:12:49.000
why didn't you speak up

00:12:49.720 --> 00:12:52.040
outside the manor just now?

00:12:54.680 --> 00:12:55.760
What are you afraid of?

00:12:57.640 --> 00:12:58.760
Or

00:12:59.120 --> 00:13:01.000
is there something

00:13:01.280 --> 00:13:03.120
the heiress of Lord Yi
is trying to hide?

00:13:04.360 --> 00:13:05.160
How dare you!

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:11.440
I never said I was Ji Qingci.

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:13.400
But Father said I am,

00:13:13.560 --> 00:13:14.720
so I am.

00:13:21.920 --> 00:13:23.360
Also, my dear sister,

00:13:24.040 --> 00:13:25.920
do you really think hiring a few bandits

00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:27.880
will be enough to kill me?

00:13:28.360 --> 00:13:30.920
Do you honestly believe
pushing me into the river

00:13:30.920 --> 00:13:32.120
will guarantee your scheme?

00:13:34.200 --> 00:13:35.360
What nonsense are you talking about?

00:13:44.800 --> 00:13:45.760
I won't let the same incident

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:47.560
happen again.

00:13:48.280 --> 00:13:50.000
If you don't believe me, try me.

00:14:08.000 --> 00:14:09.520
Remember to put ointment
on your face later.

00:14:25.720 --> 00:14:28.280
=Twin Fates=
=End of Episode 3=

00:14:29.520 --> 00:14:33.440
♪In a world of sorrows,
every encounter is fleeting♪

00:14:35.440 --> 00:14:39.320
♪Life is short
but slumber is long on Penglai Island♪

00:14:41.320 --> 00:14:45.840
♪In dreams, mountains and flowers are
as beautiful as jade♪

00:14:47.080 --> 00:14:51.120
♪All I ever wish for
is an old friend's return♪

00:14:53.080 --> 00:14:56.920
♪Majestic as a soaring dragon,
veiling the sun with drifting clouds♪

00:14:58.920 --> 00:15:02.680
♪Graceful as a flying swan goose,
breaking through snow and peril♪

00:15:04.760 --> 00:15:09.640
♪Twenty years forsaken,
I lived the life of an outlaw♪

00:15:10.480 --> 00:15:14.320
♪On the Ximo River,
who was left behind?♪

00:15:14.800 --> 00:15:20.680
♪Bit by bit,
reality shatters my only hope♪

00:15:21.200 --> 00:15:26.520
♪Layer by layer, cold blades roll up
the light I once glimpsed in secret♪

00:15:26.520 --> 00:15:29.320
♪Letters have long since yellowed♪

00:15:29.680 --> 00:15:33.080
♪Leaving only two lonely lines♪

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:38.440
♪Even the old yard is covered
with frost♪

00:15:38.440 --> 00:15:43.360
♪Pair after pair,
swallows draw my envious gaze♪

00:15:44.440 --> 00:15:50.120
♪Scene after scene,
in dreams I cannot reach♪

00:15:50.120 --> 00:15:52.720
♪While you rest beneath the earth♪

00:15:52.720 --> 00:15:56.320
♪My love lingers in this frosty world♪

00:15:57.120 --> 00:16:04.960
♪How are you now?♪